ify the design procedure for complicated\nmultifunctional optical elements and or scatterer array-based volume optics\nbased on a specified figure of merit.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 16 Jun 2018 16:49:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-27"}
