noptimal bounds for the number of gates in a depth-$d$ threshold circuit\ncomputing Parity on average, and show average-case lower bounds for threshold\nformulas of any depth.\n  Our techniques include adaptive random restrictions, anti-concentration and\nthe structural theory of linear threshold functions, and bounded-read Chernoff\nbounds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 16 Jun 2018 20:32:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-19"}
